# {{projectName}}

A production-ready REST API built with [DartAPI](https://pub.dev/packages/dartapi) — a FastAPI-inspired framework for Dart.

**Features at a glance:**
- JWT authentication (access + refresh tokens, revocation / logout)
- Full CRUD for Users and Products
- Paginated list endpoints
- Per-route response caching (5-minute TTL on product list)
- Background tasks (post-response async work)
- Rate limiting, request timeouts, Gzip compression
- Prometheus metrics (`GET /metrics`)
- Health check (`GET /health`)
- Swagger UI (`GET /docs`) + ReDoc (`GET /redoc`) + OpenAPI 3.0 spec
- Structured JSON logging
- PostgreSQL with Flyway-style migrations
- Multi-environment config (dev / staging / UAT / production)
- AOT native binary support (`dartapi build`)
- Multi-core server (`dartapi run --isolates=N`)

