## Prerequisites

- [Dart SDK](https://dart.dev/get-dart) ≥ 3.0
- PostgreSQL (or use the in-memory repositories for development without a DB)
- `dartapi` CLI (optional but recommended):

```bash
dart pub global activate dartapi
```

