## Environment Variables Reference

| Variable | Dev default | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `APP_ENV` | `dev` | Active environment: `dev` / `staging` / `uat` / `production` |
| `PORT` | `8080` | HTTP server port |
| `DEBUG` | `true` | Print startup info (`false` in production) |
| `LOG_LEVEL` | `debug` | `debug` / `info` / `warn` / `error` |
| `LOG_FORMAT` | `text` | `text` for human-readable, `json` for structured machine-readable |
| `DB_HOST` | `localhost` | PostgreSQL host |
| `DB_PORT` | `5432` | PostgreSQL port |
| `DB_NAME` | `{{projectName}}_dev` | Database name |
| `DB_USER` | `postgres` | Database user |
| `DB_PASSWORD` | `yourpassword` | **Change in production** |
| `DB_POOL_SIZE` | `5` (dev), `20` (prod) | Max connection pool size |
| `JWT_ACCESS_SECRET` | *(dev placeholder)* | Min 32 chars. **Must be changed in production** |
| `JWT_REFRESH_SECRET` | *(dev placeholder)* | Min 32 chars. **Must be changed in production** |
| `JWT_ACCESS_EXPIRY_MINUTES` | `60` (dev), `15` (prod) | Access token lifetime |
| `JWT_REFRESH_EXPIRY_DAYS` | `30` (dev), `7` (prod) | Refresh token lifetime |
| `CORS_ORIGIN` | `*` (dev), `''` (prod) | Allowed CORS origin (`*` = any, `''` = same-origin only) |
| `RATE_LIMIT_MAX` | `100` | Max requests per window per IP |
| `RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW_SECONDS` | `60` | Rate-limit window in seconds |
| `REQUEST_TIMEOUT_SECONDS` | `30` | Per-request timeout in seconds |
| `ISOLATES` | `1` | Number of server isolates (set >1 for multi-core) |

