## Database Migrations

Migration files in `migrations/` are run in lexicographic order on startup via
`MigrationRunner`. Applied migrations are tracked in `_dartapi_migrations` so
each file runs exactly once.

```bash
# Generate a new numbered migration file
dartapi generate migration add_column_to_users

# Apply all pending migrations manually
dartapi db migrate

# Preview without applying
dartapi db migrate --dry-run
```

