- [ ] Replace `JWT_ACCESS_SECRET` and `JWT_REFRESH_SECRET` with cryptographically random values (`openssl rand -hex 32`)
- [ ] Set `APP_ENV=production`
- [ ] Set `DEBUG=false`
- [ ] Set `LOG_FORMAT=json` for structured logging (Datadog, GCP Logging, ELK)
- [ ] Set `CORS_ORIGIN` to your actual frontend origin (not `*`)
- [ ] Restrict `DB_USER` to the minimum required permissions
- [ ] Enable TLS termination (nginx / load balancer in front of this service)
- [ ] Point Prometheus at `GET /metrics`
- [ ] Set `ISOLATES` to the number of available CPU cores
- [ ] Compile to a native binary: `dartapi build --docker`
